#### [NEW] [gemini_client.py](file:///D:/AutoCutAIVideo/backend/core/gemini_client.py)

Áp dụng pattern từ reference repo (`requestGeminiJsonWithParts`):

```python
class GeminiClient:
    """Client Gemini API — pattern từ Be_Fe_prompt_affvideo"""

    async def request_json(self, prompt: str, ...) -> dict
    async def request_json_with_parts(self, parts: list, ...) -> dict
    async def analyze_video(self, video_path: Path, prompt: str) -> dict

    # Internal
    def _parse_json_response(self, raw: str) -> dict  # strip code fence
    def _video_to_base64_parts(self, path: Path) -> list  # chunk if needed
```

Key patterns từ reference:
- URL: `https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/models/{model}:generateContent?key={api_key}`
- Body: `{ contents: [{ parts }], generationConfig: { temperature, topP, maxOutputTokens, responseMimeType } }`
- Response: `data.candidates[0].content.parts[].text`
- Parse: Strip code fence → try JSON.parse → extract `{...}` fallback

---

#### [NEW] [video_analyzer.py](file:///D:/AutoCutAIVideo/backend/core/video_analyzer.py)

Phân tích video multimodal (giống `analyzeTikTokWithGemini`):

```python
class VideoAnalyzer:
    async def analyze(self, video_path: Path, api_key: str) -> VideoAnalysis:
        """Gửi video + prompt phân tích cho Gemini"""
        # 1. Convert video to base64 (chunk nếu > 20MB)
        # 2. Build analysis prompt
        # 3. Call gemini_client.request_json_with_parts()
        # 4. Parse và validate kết quả

    async def analyze_batch(self, videos: list[Path], api_key: str) -> list[VideoAnalysis]:
        """Phân tích nhiều video song song"""
```

Output `VideoAnalysis`:
- `scenes`: List scene với timestamp, description, mood, quality_score (1-10)
- `highlights`: Khoảnh khắc nổi bật
- `pacing`, `color_mood`, `audio_energy`
- `suggested_cuts`: Điểm cắt gợi ý
- `content_type`: Loại nội dung

---

#### [NEW] [edit_planner.py](file:///D:/AutoCutAIVideo/backend/core/edit_planner.py)

AI lên kế hoạch edit:

```python
class EditPlanner:
    async def create_plan(
        self,
        analyses: list[VideoAnalysis],
        style: str,          # "tiktok" | "youtube" | "instagram"
        target_duration: int, # seconds
        aspect_ratio: str,    # "9:16" | "16:9" | "1:1"
        api_key: str,
    ) -> EditPlan:
        """Gửi tất cả analysis cho Gemini → nhận edit plan"""
```

Output `EditPlan`:
- `clips`: Thứ tự clip + timestamp cắt
- `transitions`: Loại transition (fade, cut, slide, zoom)
- `text_overlays`: Text + position + timing
- `color_grading`: Color preset per segment
- `speed_effects`: Slow-mo, speed ramp positions
- `music_suggestion`: Gợi ý nhịp nhạc

---

#### [NEW] [video_editor.py](file:///D:/AutoCutAIVideo/backend/core/video_editor.py)

Thực thi edit plan:
- `trim_clip()` — Cắt theo timestamp
- `merge_clips()` — Ghép clips
- `add_transition()` — Fade, dissolve, slide, wipe
- `add_text_overlay()` — Text với font, animation
- `apply_color_grade()` — Brightness, contrast, saturation
- `speed_ramp()` — Slow-mo, fast-forward
- `resize_crop()` — Resize theo aspect ratio
- `add_background_music()` — Mix audio

