#### [NEW] [schemas.py](file:///D:/AutoCutAIVideo/backend/models/schemas.py)

Pydantic models cho API:

```python
class UploadResponse(BaseModel):
    project_id: str
    videos: list[VideoInfo]

class AnalyzeRequest(BaseModel):
    project_id: str
    api_key: str
    model: str = "gemini-2.5-flash"

class AnalyzeResponse(BaseModel):
    analyses: list[VideoAnalysis]

class EditRequest(BaseModel):
    project_id: str
    api_key: str
    style: str           # "tiktok" | "youtube" | "instagram"
    target_duration: int
    aspect_ratio: str
    model: str = "gemini-2.5-flash"

class EditResponse(BaseModel):
    plan: EditPlan
    output_video_url: str
    progress_ws_url: str
```

---

#### API Endpoints

| Method | Path | Mô tả |
|--------|------|--------|
| `POST` | `/api/upload` | Upload nhiều video files |
| `POST` | `/api/analyze` | AI phân tích tất cả video |
| `POST` | `/api/edit` | Tạo edit plan + render video |
| `GET` | `/api/export/{project_id}` | Download video đã render |
| `GET` | `/api/project/{project_id}` | Lấy thông tin project |
| `DELETE` | `/api/project/{project_id}` | Xóa project |
| `WS` | `/ws/progress/{project_id}` | Real-time progress |

