## Workflow người dùng

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend (Vite)
    participant BE as Backend (FastAPI)
    participant AI as Gemini AI
    participant FF as FFmpeg

    User->>FE: Drop 4 videos + nhập API key
    FE->>BE: POST /api/upload (multipart)
    BE-->>FE: project_id + video info

    User->>FE: Chọn style TikTok 9:16, 30s
    FE->>BE: POST /api/analyze
    BE->>AI: Gemini multimodal (video + prompt)
    AI-->>BE: Video analysis JSON
    BE-->>FE: Analysis results (via WS)

    FE->>BE: POST /api/edit
    BE->>AI: Gemini (plan edit dựa trên analysis)
    AI-->>BE: Edit plan JSON
    BE->>FF: Execute edit plan
    FF-->>BE: Rendered video
    BE-->>FE: Progress + output URL (via WS)

    User->>FE: Download / Preview video
    FE->>BE: GET /api/export/{id}
    BE-->>FE: Video file stream
```

## Verification Plan

### Backend
```bash
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
python main.py  # Start FastAPI on :8000

# Test API
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/api/upload -F "files=@video1.mp4" -F "files=@video2.mp4"
```

### Frontend
```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev  # Start Vite on :5173
```

### Integration Test
1. Mở `http://localhost:5173`
2. Drop 2-4 video
3. Nhập API key → chọn style → click Analyze
4. Xem analysis → click Edit
5. Download video output
